<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xml:id="b1939_07_24_an_SraffaPiero"><teiHeader><fileDesc> <titleStmt> <title>Von <persName key="WittgensteinLudwig" role="sender" full="yes">Ludwig Wittgenstein</persName> an <persName key="SraffaPiero" role="recipient" full="yes">Piero Sraffa</persName>, 24. 7. 1939</title> <author>Wittgenstein, Ludwig</author> </titleStmt> <editionStmt n="bw2"> <edition>2. Auflage</edition> </editionStmt> <publicationStmt> <p>Ludwig Wittgenstein: Gesamtbriefwechsel, 2. Auflage</p> </publicationStmt> <sourceDesc default="false"> <p>Abschrift McGuinness, Kopie in BA.  Publiziert (WiC, S. 306).</p> </sourceDesc> </fileDesc><encodingDesc><p>TEI P5</p></encodingDesc><revisionDesc><list type="simple"><item>2010/05/15: Added to the collection</item><item>2018/12: Added to Innsbruck Correspondence Edition</item></list></revisionDesc></teiHeader><text><body><div org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" type="transcript"> <div type="address" org="uniform" sample="complete" part="N"> <p rend="right">24.7.39</p> </div> <div type="maintext" org="uniform" sample="complete" part="N"> <p rend="indent">Dear Sraffa! This is only to say that things over here went very badly. I’m leaving tomorrow for Zurich where conferences continue. It’s as hot as hell here &amp; reminds me in many other ways of that place too.</p> <p rend="indent">Ever yours </p> <p rend="indent">Ludwig Wittgenstein </p> </div> <div type="postscript" org="uniform" sample="complete" part="N"> <p rend="indent">My address: Poste Restante Zurich</p> </div> </div></body></text></TEI>